Line5.789BF: At the end of his bloody trail. This way.
VoiceDir5.789BF: Pointing at the trail of blood. Confident. Eager for revenge.
Line23.789BF: Horadrim. We were about to finish without you.
VoiceDir21.6D03F: Out of breath (he ran all the way here.) Determined to find Elias.
Line21.6D03F: He's still alive? Where is he?
VoiceDir19.789BF: Calm. Dark. She wants Elias to be afraid.
Line19.789BF: I lost him in the tunnels, but the swamp has him now.
